title: AHS 1984 Episode 3 Review & Synopsis
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Thank you all for your patience with this upload. Copyright strikes are a necessary evil.
I’m really starting to think this whole thing is like a social experiment or something Kind of like the “Whitebear” episode of black mirror

What if? .....what if none of this is happening-no Mr.Jingles,no Richard Rameriz, nobody really dead...not even a Madison movie....what if all of this going on is a Campfire tale being told by the counselors to the children/teens by by the fire to scare them...maybe???
Ray really had it coming in this episode. No redeeming qualities in his character. Like he couldn't call 911 when Chan fell down the stairs?? 😑
